Introduction

Base URL: http://127.0.0.1:8000

This documentation aims to provide all the information you need to work with our API.

As you scroll, you'll see code examples for working with the API in different programming languages in the dark area to the right (or as part of the content on mobile). You can switch the language used with the tabs at the top right (or from the nav menu at the top left on mobile).

Authenticating requests

This API is not authenticated.

Adisyonlar

Adisyonlar Listesi

Example request:
curl --request GET \
    --get "http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/business/adission" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json"
const url = new URL(
    "http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/business/adission"
);

const headers = {
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "GET",
    headers,
}).then(response => response.json());

Example response (401):

Show headers 
cache-control: no-cache, private
content-type: application/json
access-control-allow-origin: *
 

{
    "message": "Unauthenticated."
}
Received response:
Request failed with error:


Tip: Check that you're properly connected to the network.
If you're a maintainer of ths API, verify that your API is running and you've enabled CORS.
You can check the Dev Tools console for debugging information.

Adisyona Ürün Satışı Ekleme

Example request:
curl --request POST \
    "http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/business/adission/1/sale/add" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json" \
    --data "{
    \"product_id\": \"cum\",
    \"personel_id\": \"doloremque\",
    \"payment_type_id\": \"eum\",
    \"amount\": \"enim\",
    \"price\": \"quasi\"
}"

const url = new URL(
    "http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/business/adission/1/sale/add"
);

const headers = {
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

let body = {
    "product_id": "cum",
    "personel_id": "doloremque",
    "payment_type_id": "eum",
    "amount": "enim",
    "price": "quasi"
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "POST",
    headers,
    body: JSON.stringify(body),
}).then(response => response.json());

Example response (401):

Show headers 
cache-control: no-cache, private
content-type: application/json
access-control-allow-origin: *
 

{
    "message": "Unauthenticated."
}
Received response:
Request failed with error:


Tip: Check that you're properly connected to the network.
If you're a maintainer of ths API, verify that your API is running and you've enabled CORS.
You can check the Dev Tools console for debugging information.

Adisyon Ödeme Detayı

Bu apide dönen response isPermission true olarak gelmiş ise parapuan yükleme alanı görünecek. Oradan da kayıt apisine isPoint true veya false zorunlu olarak gönderilecek. default olarak false alınacak

Example request:
curl --request GET \
    --get "http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/business/adission/1/payment" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json"
const url = new URL(

  • categoryId |required | hizmetin category id si gelecek buradan
  • subCategoryId |required | hizmetin sub_category id si gelecek buradan
  • time |required | hizmetin süresi gelecek buradan
  • price |required | hizmetin fiyatı gelecek buradan

    "http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/business/business-service/add" \

    --header "Accept: application/json" \

    --data "{
    \"typeId\": \"eum\",
    \"categoryId\": \"modi\",
    \"subCategoryId\": \"et\",
    \"time\": \"consequatur\",
    \"price\": \"labore\"
}"

);

POST api/cart/save

  • Bearer Token | required | Kullanıcı Tokeni
  • name | string | required | Kartınızın Adı
  • cvc | number | required | CVC kodu
  • number | string | required | Kart Numarası
  • month | string | required | Ay Bilgisi
  • year | string | required | Yıl Bilgisi
  • name_on_the_card | string | required | Kart Üzerindeki isim
  • is_default | numeric | required | Varsayılan Kart seçimi is_default == 0 "seçili değil" is_default == 1 "seçili"

Kullanıcı kart kayıt Apisi

Example request:
curl --request POST \
    "http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/business/cart/save" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json" \
    --data "{
    \"name\": \"ytngldharxol\",
    \"number\": 89,
    \"month\": 1,
    \"year\": 1,
    \"cvc\": \"1376\",
    \"name_on_the_card\": \"mrjilnxyz\",
    \"is_default\": \"0\"
}"

const url = new URL(
    "http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/business/cart/save"
);

const headers = {
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

let body = {
    "name": "ytngldharxol",
    "number": 89,
    "month": 1,
    "year": 1,
    "cvc": "1376",
    "name_on_the_card": "mrjilnxyz",
    "is_default": "0"
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "POST",
    headers,
    body: JSON.stringify(body),
}).then(response => response.json());

POST api/detail-setup/step-1/update

  • Bearer Token
  • officialName | string | required | Salon Sahibinin adı
  • businessName | string | required | Salon Adı
  • offDay | numeric | required | kapalı olduğu günün id si
  • businessType | numeric | required | işletme türü id'si
  • cityId | string | required | Şehir
  • districtId | string | required | İlçe
  • phone | string | required | İşletme Telefon Numarası
  • email | string | required | İşletme E-posta Adresi
  • commission | string | required | P. Kredi kartı kesintisi | örneğin (10, 20, 30,40)
  • appointmentRange | string | required | Randevu aralığı | örneğin (10, 20, 30,40)
  • personalCount | string | required | Personel Sayısı | örneğin (1, 3, 5,10)
  • aboutText | string | required| İşletme Hakkında Yazısı
  • startTime | string | required| İşletme Açılış Saati Örneğin (12:08)
  • endTime | string | required| İşletme Kapanış Saati Örneğin (18:08)
  • year | date | required| Kuruluş Tarihi örneğin (2023-04-01)
  • address | text | required| Address Metni
  • logo | file | required| işletme logo
  • images | file | required| işletme görselleri

Example request:
curl --request POST \
    "http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/business/cost" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json" \
    --data "{
    \"costCategoryId\": \"ducimus\",
    \"personelId\": \"aut\",
    \"paymentTypeId\": \"accusantium\",
    \"price\": \"quia\",
    \"operationDate\": \"2024-07-04T16:18:51\"
}"

const url = new URL(
    "http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/business/cost"
);

const headers = {
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

let body = {
    "costCategoryId": "ducimus",
    "personelId": "aut",
    "paymentTypeId": "accusantium",
    "price": "quia",
    "operationDate": "2024-07-04T16:18:51"
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "POST",
    headers,
    body: JSON.stringify(body),
}).then(response => response.json());

POST api/personal/add

Personel Ekleme pointi
Gerekli alanlar

  • token
  • name |required | string |
  • image |required | string |
  • email |required | string |
  • phone |required | string |
  • password |required | string |
  • approveType |required | numeric | örneğin 1 veya 0
  • restDay |required | numeric | haftanın günlerinden herhangi bir günün id si
  • startTime |required | string | örneğin 10:43
  • endTime |required | string | örneğin 10:43
  • foodStart |required | string | örneğin 10:43
  • foodEnd |required | string | örneğin 10:43
  • gender |required | numeric | 1 => kadın,2 => erkek,3 => Unisex herhangi biri
  • rate |required | numeric | 10 personel yüzdesi 10 = %10
  • appointmentRange |required | numeric | randevu aralığı örneğin "15" dk bazında
  • description |required | string
  • services | required | array | eğer tümü seçeneği seçilirse "all" olarak gönderebilirsiniz dizi içerisinde
Example request:
curl --request POST \
    "http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/business/personal/add" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json" \
    --header "Bearer: {token}" \
    --data "{
    \"name\": \"enim\",
    \"email\": \"nesciunt\",
    \"phone\": \"nam\",
    \"password\": \"non\",
    \"approveType\": \"doloribus\",
    \"restDay\": \"commodi\",
    \"startTime\": \"ab\",
    \"endTime\": \"cumque\",
    \"gender\": \"nam\",
    \"rate\": \"ipsam\",
    \"appointmentRange\": \"ab\",
    \"description\": \"dolores\",
    \"services\": \"quaerat\"
}"

const url = new URL(
    "http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/business/personal/add"
);

const headers = {
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
    "Bearer": "{token}",
};

let body = {
    "name": "enim",
    "email": "nesciunt",

POST api/setup/update

  • Bearer Token | required | İşletme Kategorisi
  • category_id | string | required | İşletme Kategorisi
  • name | string | required | İşletme Adı
  • type_id | string | required | Hizmet Türü businessTypes değişkeninden alabilirsiniz
  • city_id | string | required | Şehir
  • district_id | string | required | İlçe
  • off_day_id | string | required | Kapalı Olduğu Gün
  • phone | string | required | Kullanıcı Telefon Numarası
  • about_content | string | required| İşletme Hakkında Yazısı
  • start_time | string | required| İşletme Açılış Saati Örneğin (12:08)
  • end_time | string | required| İşletme Kapanış Saati Örneğin (18:08)
  • latitude | string | required| Haritadan seçilen lat bilgisi
  • longitude | string | required| Haritadan seçilen long bilgisi
  • address | text | required| Address Metni
  • package_id | integer or string | required| Seçili Paket idsi

}"

);

    "Accept": "application/json",
};

    "branchName": "accusamus",
    "officialId": "nisi"
